sql_result.sql: WITH base AS (SELECT DISTINCT student.id, student.student_no, student.real_name, student.class_id FROM student JOIN score ON student.id = score.student_id JOIN attendance ON student.id = attendance.student_id WHERE student.status = '在读' AND score.score_value < 60 AND attendance.status = '缺勤' AND student.is_deleted = 0 AND score.is_deleted = 0 AND attendance.is_deleted = 0) SELECT base.id, base.student_no, base.real_name, base.class_id FROM base
